  }, {
    "id": "s4",
    "n_params": 0,
    "step_txt": "\nNow right hand side expression of the given equation is\n\\[\n\t\\textrm{RHS } = \\frac{(xk + yk )^2 + (x + y )^2}{(xk + yk ) + (x + y )}\n\\]"
  }, {
    "id": "s5",
