  }, {
    "id": "s6",
    "n_params": 0,
    "step_txt": "\nFrom the above two expressions we can clearly observe that\n\\[\n\t\\textrm{LHS } = \\textrm{ RHS}\n\\]\nHence proved.\n\\newline\n"
  }]
};
